						<summary>

						<p>c. 13th-14th Century.</p>						

						<p>Damaged badly. Seems to record an asylum deed given to the <hi rend="italic">ūr-kaṇmāḷar</hi> of both the wings of Peruṅgaḷūr in Teṉ-panaṅgāḍu-nāḍu by some <hi rend="italic">kaṇmāḷar.</hi> The concluding details are lost.</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">IPS</hi>, No. 965.] </p>						

